<div class="content" name="FAX_EVENT_JOB_1" uuid="41bc64b0-9bfa-433e-922f-ce695af0b89d"><p>The <b>FAX_EVENT_JOB_1</b> structure defines information
about notifications regarding a single job in the server&#39;s <a href="46aba9c4-ebb1-4b10-86ac-4bb3025657b9#gt_c1a6400d-703b-4f9a-a74c-40f1487978d9" data-linktype="relative-path">queue</a>. This structure is
